latestIgtvVideos.title: Body positivity for men? My truth.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This is me opening up to all of you and talking about my insecurities. I’ve kept this part of my life hidden from everyone! I’ve always felt invalidated especially when I talk about my insecurities. Today, a body positivity influencer (male) is someone who only talks about getting ripped. I see almost no male influencer talking about self acceptance and body positivity. I’ve had no one to look upto and maybe that’s why I’m putting this out for everyone to know that they’re not alone. I am definitely not on the other side and still insecure af but all I’ve learnt over the years is that I’m allowed to hold hands with the darkness and still heal. Please be kind to others because your words can leave scars. 

#bodypositivity #insecure #ocd #malebodypositivity #6pack #bodypositive #selflove #igtvvideos #igtvcommunity #mentalillness #mentalhealthawareness #malementalhealth #igtvindia #bodydysmorphia #beautymyth

latestPosts.caption:
The Most beautiful reel you’ll see today! 

I was in tears when I read Arvey’s note for her. He was so much in pain yet he wanted his mother to live the best life. From hopping on a flight to Mumbai to learning how to drive an automatic, even doing a full-blown brand photoshoot with @mywishcare and ending the day with a celebration of hitting 500K followers - @internetkimummy is truly living her best life and making her son (and all of us!) super proud! 

This Mother’s Day, we’re celebrating moms who hustle, who grow, and who show up — even when it’s not easy which is why @mywishcare and I decided to do this together for her. @mywishcare isn’t just a skincare brand - it stands for every woman who juggles 10 roles at once. Whether you’re a mom, a daughter, a boss, or all three - their simple, effective skincare products fit perfectly into your non-stop day.

Here’s your reminder to cheer for the women in your life and remind them how far they’ve come.

It’s your turn, Maa! 

I know you’ve compromised a lot for our dreams and I wish it wasn’t that way for you. I see, as an adult man, how much you’ve given to us and how difficult it has been for you. Despite your hardships and sacrifices, you have always kept your cool. You are the OG cooler of our home - the person who soothes us and  binds us despite all odds!
However, I’m so glad you have the courage to dream again, fight for it and begin Bliss Interiors with your bestie.

Thank you @symphonylimited for working on this special day with me and sending your #thandithandirimjhimcooling for her. You guys know how to keep it cool just like maa. 

If your mother sacrificed  her dreams too, don’t only thank her but encourage her to dream again.
